{"tid":1242822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[急] 日本 G20 示威請遠離疆獨藏獨東帝汶獨立分子","createTime":"2019-06-19T08:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T14:48:57.000Z","uid":192798,"like":13,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3d956429f34ab2e45886d46ddc3553ebd47dcbf2","tid":1242822,"uid":192798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:05:25.000Z","msg":"我真係好著急，陳雲 hater 請放下成見。<br />\n<br />\n//陳雲：香港的共匪已經在G20佈局破壞是次請願。例如要香港請願者加入亞洲殖民地疆獨藏獨東帝汶獨立之類恐怖組織陣營之內示威，搞壞香港請願者的聲譽，也令日後香港的請願者到其他外國示威的時候，會被外國政府納入恐怖主義獨立份子來防範和規管。<br />\n香港已經有一個自投羅網的恐怖主義政綱被香港政府查封的政黨準備去日本，用港獨玩死香港。美國要香港普選，達到自治，之後保護獨立關稅區的地位。美國不是要香港獨立，因為香港已經幾乎是個國家。普選之後就是完全自治。<br />\n這些偽港獨自決之類的共匪，是香港人，他們會在東帝汶獨立組織之類的旁邊，舉起港獨標語。他們不是北京的，但做起事來，比起北京更惡毒。不過，也要告訴各位，這些共匪，是香港人自己有份資助和養大的。//"},{"pid":"3ba76f01f091c073deb22554983a8770fc7641d1","tid":1242822,"uid":166706,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:10:31.000Z","msg":"東帝汶咪獨左立囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有恐怖份子?"},{"pid":"91ada3160acac5b4428e8212b7594288ef3299d6","tid":1242822,"uid":57569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:10:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab955b02d52d2cd517d5d3009e44f1779b0e37a8","tid":1242822,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:10:58.000Z","msg":"借個post擺下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ynR8uYb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FynR8uYb.png&h=86b956d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kj8Scbx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKj8Scbx.png&h=d687ab09&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b4HjBDd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb4HjBDd.png&h=4bd4549e&s={SIZE}\